  "prompt": "Is there hostel in SIG?",
  "response": "The availability of a hostel at \"SIG\" depends on which specific institution or organization you're referring to, as \"SIG\" could stand for multiple entities. For example:\n\n1. **Surana Institute of Graduate Studies (SIG), India**: This institution typically offers hostel facilities for students. If this is the SIG you're asking about, you should contact the institute directly or check their official website for details on accommodation options.\n\n2. **Other SIGs (e.g., Summer Institute of Linguistics, Shanghai International Group, or a company)**: These may not provide hostel facilities unless explicitly stated. \n\nTo give a precise answer, please clarify the full name or context of \"SIG.\" If it\u2019s an educational institution, hostels are often available, but confirming with the organization directly is recommended.",
